{
  "id": "RAW_798b459a",
  "title": "斯坦福、英伟达和伯克利提出具身 Test-Time Scaling Law",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2650995270&idx=3&sn=22bcd784ab1113869240b9f8b289ce5c",
  "date": "2025-10-14 05:43:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">本文的第一作者为斯坦福大学博士生 Jacky Kwok。共同通讯作者包括英伟达自动驾驶研究总监 Marco Pavone、斯坦福大学计算机系教授兼 DeepMind 科学家 Azalia Mirhoseini，以及 UC 伯克利教授 Ion Stoica。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Vision-Language-Action（VLA）模型在视觉运动控制中展现出了卓越能力，但如何在复杂的真实世界中保持鲁棒性仍是一个长期挑战。研究团队展示了一个关键发现：在推理阶段，结合「生成 - 验证」（generate-and-verify）范式从而增加计算量（test-time compute）可以显著提升 VLA 模型的泛化能力与可靠性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与此同时，论文系统性地探讨了具身智能中的 Test-Time Scaling Law：随着推理阶段的采样与验证规模增长，VLA 模型在任务成功率和稳定性方面呈现出可预测的提升规律。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510876\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.254249815225425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1353\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rd1icibqT8IwpKictO0YzvNy1kol3Z3Nz4Aicw6vO35icNtI61N6Od1XhC2dQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"143\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0046ed4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rd1icibqT8IwpKictO0YzvNy1kol3Z3Nz4Aicw6vO35icNtI61N6Od1XhC2dQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：RoboMonkey: Scaling Test-Time Sampling and Verification for Vision-Language-Action Models</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.17811\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.17811</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">代码链接：robomonkey-vla.github.io</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">作者邮箱：jackykwok@stanford.edu</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">接收会议：CoRL 2025</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">具身 Test-Time Scaling Law</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510877\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.315625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdwsgLYsHYEgAvESia9hibhnxonyK5VQlyricjKAEV8NvvicJFiapswib9ep5w/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"178\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d99fb553&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdwsgLYsHYEgAvESia9hibhnxonyK5VQlyricjKAEV8NvvicJFiapswib9ep5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">团队通过大量实验发现：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">当在推理阶段增加候选动作的生成数量时，VLA 的动作误差会持续下降</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。具体来说，无论是反复从机器人策略模型中采样动作、对部分采样动作施加高斯扰动，还是在离散动作空间中进行随机采样，这些方法在有「理想验证器」（oracle verifier）的前提下，都能显著优于单次推理的 OpenVLA 基线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">团队还揭示出一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">幂律规律</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（power law）：在多种主流 VLA 模型（包括 CogACT、Octo、OpenVLA 和 SpatialVLA）中，动作误差与高斯扰动采样数量之间呈现出稳定的幂律关系。这意味着，机器人控制问题不应仅仅被视为一个「生成」任务；相反，生成候选动作 + 验证筛选的范式，能在不改动训练模型的前提下显著提升性能。研究者希望这一发现能够推动动作验证器（scalable action verifiers）的发展，为通用机器人模型提供更稳健的落地路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">核心问题</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在提出具身 Test-Time Scaling Law 之后，研究团队进一步聚焦于三个关键问题：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">验证器训练</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：是否能够利用训练得到的动作验证器（action verifier）来替代 oracle verifier，以提升 VLA 的稳定性？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">合成数据扩展</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：能否构建大规模合成数据来训练验证器，从而推动下游任务的性能提升？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">实际部署可行性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：如何设计高效的算法与系统，使 test-time scaling 在真实机器人上实现低延迟、可扩展的部署？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">方法概述</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阶段一・动作验证器训练</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510878\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.16267547481420314\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2422\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rd9OqG9X7RMNBVuTrRpOJjFJDkribKwqyCenXlvrlp6ibW386trO683QTg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"92\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cc5d8d60&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rd9OqG9X7RMNBVuTrRpOJjFJDkribKwqyCenXlvrlp6ibW386trO683QTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究者首先利用机器人数据集，用 VLA 为每个状态采样 N 个候选动作，并通过聚类将其压缩为 K 个具有代表性的动作。随后，基于候选动作与真实动作（ground truth action） 的&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">RMSE 差异构造合成偏好数据</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（synthetic action preference dataset），并用其微调一个基于 VLM 的动作验证器 （VLM-based verifier），赋予模型对动作优劣的判别能力。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该验证器的训练损失函数遵循 Bradley-Terry 模型，并在此基础上加入了对偏好强度（preference levels）的修正项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510880\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07356948228882834\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1835\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdzXXy2Lz6WFdw8vElicR7QNXbib2kE51sic8byP595UervyPaqJrnH0vzA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"41\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6d926f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdzXXy2Lz6WFdw8vElicR7QNXbib2kE51sic8byP595UervyPaqJrnH0vzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阶段二・推理阶段的计算扩展</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510879\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23208191126279865\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1758\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdQ7Z2PxvR3beiboSoawJEsh7Ok8Fg67P2YKN6GcA1wO3WU3JFJsHTcpA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"131\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e3d47aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdQ7Z2PxvR3beiboSoawJEsh7Ok8Fg67P2YKN6GcA1wO3WU3JFJsHTcpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在实际部署中，系统会根据任务指令和环境观测，用 VLA 采样&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">N̂</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;个初始动作。研究者对这些动作的平移与旋转部分</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">拟合高斯分布</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，并通过多数投票（majority voting）确定抓取器的开合状态，构建出高效的动作分布。由此便可以在几乎不增加计算开销的前提下，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">快速采样出&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">K̂</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp; 个候选动作</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。最后，利用在阶段一中训练好的 VLM 动作验证器，对这些候选动作进行评估和排序，从中挑选出最优动作执行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验结果</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510881\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6444444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 417px;height: 269px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdZycFSItOBZfYXibFb9GQZrJkndVakM6jI1ibX3rTsaOhpB9DNDLc5FZg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"417\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9704023d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdZycFSItOBZfYXibFb9GQZrJkndVakM6jI1ibX3rTsaOhpB9DNDLc5FZg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究表明将 VLA 模型与 RoboMonkey 结合可以带来显著性能提升：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在真实世界的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;out-of-distribution tasks 上 + 25%</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;in-distribution SIMPLER 环境上 + 9%</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;LIBERO-Long benchmark+7%</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些结果表明，RoboMonkey 不仅提升了整体成功率，还能在部署时有效缓解以下关键问题：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">抓取不精准&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">任务推进失败&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">碰撞问题</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510855\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3373493975903614\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a72589f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdpR43mGC91NBa0jibBt1BTibI3HsXtA8RO6hLoGCsmyZacnpS5YzNrjsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">扩展合成数据</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510882\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6688500727802038\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1374\" style=\"width: 337px;height: 225px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdsbIRbwGa8q9ibyfAuOj5S8LmAcCYQ4neCqicp4aMuiak58HAam9V07yUQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"337\" data-cropsely2=\"225\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=10bc6eed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdsbIRbwGa8q9ibyfAuOj5S8LmAcCYQ4neCqicp4aMuiak58HAam9V07yUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实验结果表明，扩展合成数据集规模对验证器性能有显著提升作用。随着数据规模逐步增加，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">RoboMonkey 验证器的准确性呈近似对数线性（log-linear）增长</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，并在 SIMPLER 环境上的成功率显著提高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">高效推理部署</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503510883\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32763671875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4096\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdd8QcZ9BRt1vCRYkMWoJbibq5DVdGktI88O2TSDicnkkLOZP6cBF1Eficw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"184\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9817bcbc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kMxZIb7Rly3twtHKsQ2rdd8QcZ9BRt1vCRYkMWoJbibq5DVdGktI88O2TSDicnkkLOZP6cBF1Eficw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了让 Test-Time Scaling 在真实系统中具备可部署性，研究团队在 SGLang 之上实现了一个专用的&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">VLA serving 引擎</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。该引擎支持高速的 VLA 动作重复采样，并通过高斯扰动高效地构建动作分布（action proposal distribution）。这一系统优化显著降低了推理阶段的开销。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，从系统架构的角度来看，RoboMonkey 在相同的延迟约束（latency target）下，如果配备了更大容量的高带宽存储器（HBM），GPU 就能够支持更高的吞吐量（throughput），从而进一步提升机器人基础模型的泛化能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">总结</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本文的主要贡献可总结如下：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">提出具身推理缩放定律</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;—— 实验证明，在多个 VLA 模型中，动作误差与采样数量之间呈现幂律关系。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">可扩展的验证器训练流程</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;—— 构建了一条自动生成动作偏好数据的方法，并基于此提出了训练 VLM 动作验证器的框架。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">验证 Test-Time Scaling 的有效性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;—— 证明了所提出的 test-time scaling 框架能够在无需重新训练 VLA 的前提下显著增强 VLA 模型的表现。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "斯坦福、英伟达和伯克利提出具身智能的“Test-Time Scaling Law”，通过推理阶段的“生成-验证”范式显著提升 VLA 模型的泛化能力和鲁棒性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "斯坦福、英伟达和伯克利提出具身智能的“Test-Time Scaling Law”，通过推理阶段的“生成-验证”范式显著提升 VLA 模型的泛化能力和鲁棒性。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了斯坦福、英伟达和伯克利团队提出的具身智能 Test-Time Scaling Law。该研究发现，在推理阶段增加计算量，即采用“生成-验证”（generate-and-verify）范式，能显著提升视觉-语言-动作（VLA）模型在复杂真实世界中的泛化能力和可靠性。论文揭示了动作误差与推理采样规模之间存在的幂律关系。为实现和验证这一定律，团队设计并构建了 RoboMonkey 框架，该框架通过利用合成数据训练 VLM 动作验证器，并在推理阶段高效采样和评估候选动作。实验结果表明，RoboMonkey 在多种任务上显著提高了 VLA 模型的成功率，并能有效解决抓取不精准、任务失败和碰撞等实际问题。此外，研究还展示了扩展合成数据对验证器性能的积极影响，并实现了高效的推理部署方案。",
